moji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9d31c4e61a40c903946296300f7310042dd5864a","tid":1630984,"uid":59818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"利伸 有個外國朋友同我講睇相見到前線淨係幫某一兩間鋪頭裝修 唔係盲目純破壞 有時落錯手仲會識say sorry 覺得示威者好理性 唔同外國嗰啲暴動"},{"pid":"18e138ffa2aa0a7ac58e4d4ade6620601beda467","tid":1630984,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"733ff082ab34d030830b7f70b15f981a6b695c10","tid":1630984,"uid":12662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:21:49.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔等埋先呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"到時過左你咪又係話等埋加埋加辣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9fc0ac1d6acd19c5ee28587540b0291e696e4b","tid":1630984,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"唔好對人權法案太大期望⋯⋯"},{"pid":"50fe1655f9c8f09174f6cda8156b478f77ab67c5","tid":1630984,"uid":201031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://edition-m.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html?r=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fasia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition-m.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%3Fr%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fedition.cnn.com%252Fasia&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6k9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=d1593257\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition-m.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%3Fr%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fedition.cnn.com%252Fasia&h=b515d05e\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition-m.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html?r=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fasia</a> <a hre